1RM test (p = 0.040) were observed in the RESEX group. No changes were observed 
for the other variables investigated.
CONCLUSIONS: In this sample of patients with schizophrenia, 20 weeks of 
resistance or concurrent exercise program improved disease symptoms, strength, 
and quality of life. ClinicalTrials.gov: NCT01674543.

