The Aging of the Global Population: The Changing Epidemiology of Disease and 
Spinal Disorders.

Fehlings MG(1), Tetreault L, Nater A, Choma T, Harrop J, Mroz T, Santaguida C, 
Smith JS.

Author information:
(1)*Division of Neurosurgery and Spine Program, Toronto Western Hospital, 
